{"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\"/><title>Share Your Job Search Experience — Job Board Scorer</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Help us understand your job search experience and improve job board recommendations.\"/><meta name=\"next-head-count\" content=\"4\"/><script async=\"\" src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-13DDMQLQFZ\"></script><script>\n                    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n                    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n                    gtag('js', new Date());\n                    gtag('config', 'G-13DDMQLQFZ', {\n                      page_path: window.location.pathname,\n                    });\n                  </script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/css/3b0c939fc99db33f.css\" as=\"style\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/3b0c939fc99db33f.css\" data-n-g=\"\"/><noscript data-n-css=\"\"></noscript><script defer=\"\" nomodule=\"\" src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-a146a8ef8f1e9d05.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/framework-e08ca35bb8c7d6c2.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-ecf9fdf2fdcbcf0c.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/pages/_app-a4b465d0d03c3032.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/pages/candidate-feedback-53e9dbf0f7c5ec9b.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/wDAhdRrE5oh3YKiYu4_Cl/_buildManifest.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/wDAhdRrE5oh3YKiYu4_Cl/_ssgManifest.js\" defer=\"\"></script></head><body><div id=\"__next\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Share Your Job Search Experience</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Your feedback helps us understand which job boards work best for job seekers. This information will improve recommendations for future candidates.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">Your Feedback</h2><form class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8\"><fieldset class=\"border rounded-lg p-6 space-y-4\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold px-2\">Contact Information</legend><div><label for=\"candidate-email-1\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Email Address <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input id=\"candidate-email-1\" type=\"email\" name=\"candidateEmail\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"your@email.com\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">We use this only to contact you about your feedback (optional follow-up).</p></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"border rounded-lg p-6 space-y-4\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold px-2\">Application Details</legend><div><label for=\"job-title-2\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Job Title You Applied For <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input id=\"job-title-2\" type=\"text\" name=\"jobTitle\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"e.g., Senior Software Engineer, Product Manager\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"board-name-3\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Which Job Board Did You Use? <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input id=\"board-name-3\" type=\"text\" name=\"jobBoardName\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"e.g., LinkedIn, Indeed, Tech Jobs Daily\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"app-status-4\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Application Outcome <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><select id=\"app-status-4\" name=\"applicationStatus\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"><option value=\"applied_only\" selected=\"\">I applied but didn&#x27;t hear back</option><option value=\"rejected\">I was rejected after applying</option><option value=\"interviewed\">I was interviewed</option><option value=\"offered\">I received an offer</option><option value=\"hired\">I was hired and started the job</option></select></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"border rounded-lg p-6 space-y-4\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold px-2\">Application Experience</legend><div><label for=\"app-exp-5\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">How easy was the application process? <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><select id=\"app-exp-5\" name=\"applicationExperience\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"><option value=\"poor\">Poor - Very complicated or confusing</option><option value=\"fair\">Fair - Somewhat difficult</option><option value=\"good\" selected=\"\">Good - Straightforward</option><option value=\"excellent\">Excellent - Very easy</option><option value=\"exceptional\">Exceptional - Best I&#x27;ve experienced</option></select></div><div><label for=\"clarity-6\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">How clear was the job posting? <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><select id=\"clarity-6\" name=\"postingClarity\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"><option value=\"poor\">Poor - Very unclear or missing info</option><option value=\"fair\">Fair - Some important details missing</option><option value=\"good\" selected=\"\">Good - Clear requirements and expectations</option><option value=\"excellent\">Excellent - Very detailed and clear</option><option value=\"exceptional\">Exceptional - Exceptionally well-written</option></select></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"border rounded-lg p-6 space-y-4\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold px-2\">Role Fit &amp; Compensation</legend><div><label for=\"fit-9\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Was the role a good fit for your skills? <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><select id=\"fit-9\" name=\"roleFit\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"><option value=\"poor\">Poor - Not aligned with my experience</option><option value=\"fair\">Fair - Some misalignment</option><option value=\"good\" selected=\"\">Good - Decent fit</option><option value=\"excellent\">Excellent - Great fit</option><option value=\"exceptional\">Exceptional - Perfect match</option></select></div><div><label for=\"salary-10\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Salary &amp; Benefits Transparency <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><select id=\"salary-10\" name=\"salaryTransparency\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"><option value=\"not_disclosed\" selected=\"\">Not disclosed - No salary range in posting</option><option value=\"insufficient\">Insufficient - Very vague range</option><option value=\"adequate\">Adequate - Reasonable range provided</option><option value=\"competitive\">Competitive - Clear and fair range</option><option value=\"excellent\">Excellent - Full transparency on package</option></select></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"border rounded-lg p-6 space-y-4\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold px-2\">Recommendation</legend><div><label for=\"hire-11\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Would you recommend this job board to other job seekers?<!-- --> <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><select id=\"hire-11\" name=\"hireBoardAgain\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"><option value=\"definitely_not\">Definitely not - Poor experience</option><option value=\"probably_not\">Probably not - More bad than good</option><option value=\"maybe\" selected=\"\">Maybe - Mixed experience</option><option value=\"probably\">Probably - Mostly positive</option><option value=\"definitely\">Definitely - Excellent job board</option></select></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"border rounded-lg p-6 space-y-4\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold px-2\">Additional Feedback</legend><div><label for=\"feedback-12\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium mb-1\">Any additional comments or suggestions?</label><textarea id=\"feedback-12\" name=\"feedbackNotes\" placeholder=\"Share your thoughts to help us improve job board recommendations...\" rows=\"4\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"></textarea><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">Your feedback is valuable and helps candidates and employers find the best job boards.</p></div></fieldset><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><button type=\"submit\" class=\"px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white transition-colors bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 active:bg-blue-800\">Submit Feedback</button></div></form></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 mb-12\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">❓</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">What We Ask</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">We ask about your application experience, job posting clarity, interview process, role fit, salary transparency, and whether you&#x27;d recommend the job board to others.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🔒</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Your Privacy</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Your email is used only for optional follow-up. All other data is anonymized and aggregated. We never sell your information to third parties.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">⭐</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">How It Helps</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Your feedback directly improves our job board recommendations. We share insights with job seekers to help them choose the best platforms for their careers.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"border-b pb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Why are you collecting this feedback?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">We&#x27;re building a system to help job seekers find the best job boards based on real candidate experiences. Your feedback is crucial for understanding which platforms work best for different types of candidates and roles.</p></div><div class=\"border-b pb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">How do you protect my privacy?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Your data is stored securely in an encrypted database and is only used in aggregate form for analysis. We never share individual survey responses with job boards or other third parties. Your email is optional and used only for feedback follow-up if you choose to provide it.</p></div><div class=\"border-b pb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">How long does this take?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Most candidates complete the survey in 3–5 minutes. The form adapts based on your answers (for example, interview questions only appear if you were interviewed).</p></div><div class=\"border-b pb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Will my employer see my feedback?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">No. Your feedback is completely anonymous to employers. We only aggregate data at the job board level, never linking feedback to your name or company. Employers have no access to survey responses.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">How is this information used?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Your feedback is aggregated with other responses to create job board efficiency scores. These scores help other candidates make informed decisions about which platforms to use. We also produce industry reports and trends based on anonymized aggregated data.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-indigo-600 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 text-center text-white\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">Help Us Improve Job Board Recommendations</h2><p class=\"text-lg mb-4\">Your experience matters. A few minutes of your time can help thousands of job seekers find better platforms.</p></div></div></div></div><script id=\"__NEXT_DATA__\" type=\"application/json\">{\"props\":{\"pageProps\":{}},\"page\":\"/candidate-feedback\",\"query\":{},\"buildId\":\"wDAhdRrE5oh3YKiYu4_Cl\",\"nextExport\":true,\"autoExport\":true,\"isFallback\":false,\"scriptLoader\":[]}</script></body></html>","isFullyStaticPage":true}